        =======
        History
        =======
        
        0.2.1 (Oct 19, 2020)
        --------------------
        
        Bug fixes
        ~~~~~~~~~
        
        * Fixed tooltip rendering for datetime axis.
        
        0.2.0 (Sep 8, 2020)
        -------------------
        
        Breaking changes
        ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
        
        * Dropped compatibility with Python 2.7 and 3.5 and bokeh versions < 2.2
        
        0.1.0 (Sep 8, 2020)
        -------------------
        
        * First official release
        * Last release compatible with Python 2.7/3.5
        
